 for =E2=80=9CGot it!=E2=80=9D and fire the test prompt from your table. If=
 output wobbles, edit the instruction and overwrite the old brick=E2=80=94n=
ever stack revisions. Review weekly: keep the bricks you used, delete the r=
est.=20
